			}
			else
			{
				bool flag2 = Operators.CompareString(this.lblCard1.Text, "", false) == 0 & Operators.CompareString(this.lblCard2.Text, "", false) == 0 & Operators.CompareString(this.lblCard3.Text, "", false) == 0 & Operators.CompareString(this.lblCard4.Text, "", false) == 0 & Operators.CompareString(this.lblCard5.Text, "", false) == 0 & Operators.CompareString(this.lblCard6.Text, "", false) == 0;

				{
					Interaction.MsgBox("     ", MsgBoxStyle.OkOnly, null);
				}
				else
				{
					bool flag3 = this.lblPort1.Text.Trim().Length == 0;
					if (flag3)
					{
						Interaction.MsgBox("    ", MsgBoxStyle.OkOnly, null);
					}
					else
					{
						bool flag4 = Conversion.Val(this.txtWorkID.Text) == 0.0;
						if (flag4)
						{
							Interaction.MsgBox("    ", MsgBoxStyle.OkOnly, null);
						}

						{

							this.DisableCntl();

						}
					}
				}
			}
		}

		// Token: 0x060009A6 RID: 2470 RVA: 0x0000B3A4 File Offset: 0x000095A4
		private void releaseObject(object obj)
		{
			try
			{
				Marshal.ReleaseComObject(RuntimeHelpers.GetObjectValue(obj));
				obj = null;
			}
			catch (Exception ex)
			{
				obj = null;
			}
			finally
			{
				bool flag = obj != null;
				if (flag)
				{
					int generation = GC.GetGeneration(RuntimeHelpers.GetObjectValue(obj));
					GC.Collect(generation);
				}
				else
				{
					GC.Collect();
					GC.WaitForPendingFinalizers();
				}
			}
		}

			}

			{
				DestNumber
			}, null, null);
			NewLateBinding.LateSet(smsobject, null, "TP_Data_Coding_Scheme", new object[]
			{
				DataCodingScheme
			}, null, null);
			NewLateBinding.LateSet(smsobject, null, "TP_Message_Reference", new object[]
			{
				0
			}, null, null);
			NewLateBinding.LateSet(smsobject, null, "TP_Validity_Period", new object[]
			{
				ValidPeriod
			}, null, null);
			NewLateBinding.LateSet(smsobject, null, "TP_User_Data", new object[]
			{
				UserData
			}, null, null);
			int num;
			bool flag = num == 0;
			string[] result;
			if (flag)
			{
				result = new string[]
				{
					Conversions.ToString(NewLateBinding.LateGet(this.SMSObject, null, "GetSMSPDUCode", new object[0], null, null, null))
				};
			}
			else
			{
				result = (string[])NewLateBinding.LateGet(this.SMSObject, null, "GetEMSPDUCode", new object[0], null, null, null);
			}
			return result;
		}

		// Token: 0x06000AAA RID: 2730 RVA: 0x000C5AAC File Offset: 0x000C3CAC
		private void txtNumberToAddinRobot_KeyPress(object sender, KeyPressEventArgs e)
		{
			bool flag = Strings.Asc(e.KeyChar) == 13;
			if (flag)
			{
				bool flag2 = this.txtNumberToAddinRobot.Text.Length != 11;
				if (flag2)
				{
					this.txtInfo.Text = "Enter ADD in sign and number here then Enter\r\n" + this.txtInfo.Text;
					this.txtInfo.Text = "To Add number\r\n" + this.txtInfo.Text;
					this.txtInfo.Text = "--------------------\r\n" + this.txtInfo.Text;
					this.txtInfo.Text = "Enter DEL in sign and number here then Enter\r\n" + this.txtInfo.Text;
					this.txtInfo.Text = "To Delete number\r\n" + this.txtInfo.Text;
					this.txtInfo.Text = "--------------------\r\n" + this.txtInfo.Text;
				}
				else
				{
					bool flag3 = Operators.CompareString(this.txtWebQrySign.Text, "ADD", false) != 0 & Operators.CompareString(this.txtWebQrySign.Text, "DEL", false) != 0;
					if (flag3)
					{
						this.txtInfo.Text = "Enter ADD in sign and number here then Enter\r\n" + this.txtInfo.Text;
						this.txtInfo.Text = "To Add number\r\n" + this.txtInfo.Text;
						this.txtInfo.Text = "--------------------\r\n" + this.txtInfo.Text;
						this.txtInfo.Text = "Enter DEL in sign and number here then Enter\r\n" + this.txtInfo.Text;
						this.txtInfo.Text = "To Delete number\r\n" + this.txtInfo.Text;
						this.txtInfo.Text = "--------------------\r\n" + this.txtInfo.Text;
					}
					else
					{
						bool flag4 = Operators.CompareString(this.txtWebQrySign.Text, "ADD", false) == 0;
						if (flag4)
						{
							this.AddNumberToRobot(this.txtNumberToAddinRobot.Text);
							this.txtRet01.Text = this.txtNumberToAddinRobot.Text + " Added\r\n" + this.txtRet01.Text;
							this.txtNumberToAddinRobot.Text = "";
						}
						else
						{
							bool flag5 = Operators.CompareString(this.txtWebQrySign.Text, "DEL", false) == 0;
							if (flag5)
							{
								this.objDataRemote.DatabaseCommand(string.Concat(new string[]
								{
									"DELETE FROM  ",
									MysqlConn.RD_name,
									"_nums where mob_number = '",
									this.txtNumberToAddinRobot.Text,
									"'"
								}));
								this.txtNumberToAddinRobot.Text = "";
								this.txtRet01.Text = this.txtNumberToAddinRobot.Text + " Deleted\r\n" + this.txtRet01.Text;
							}
						}
					}
				}
			}
		}
